.--'--'-.    Exercise 2 is also about the /etc/passwd file...

We've found some malicious hackers on our system belonging to the hacker
group circus cyber. One of them is the the user elephant_p.

The sixth field of the /etc/passwd file shows the location of the home 
directory of a user.

What is the home directory of the user 'elephant_p' on the system? 
   
